{"tid":2356173,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"東方煉獄 (原: 炎)","createTime":"2021-01-06T15:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T13:06:12.000Z","uid":6842,"like":87,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9a09ead2153f31496716ff38ae51e07d9592d369","tid":2356173,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:30:30.000Z","msg":"會否再見 隔天再戰<br />\n撲滅煉獄紅焰<br />\n就算犧牲也少不免 哪怕沒有改變<br />\n痛傷再痛 有些奮勇<br />\n最忌是有種 <br />\n若你不懂得區分對錯<br />\n留待史書中記載<br />\n<br />\n狂徒亂世 煙火槍聲 沾污夜幕時<br />\n仍同仇敵愾 苦守街邊每個夜晚<br />\n誰若志未殘 萬眾走過萬難<br />\n未到初春 再難都不折返<br />\n<br />\n退後了一格 擴大了打壓<br />\n血肉建築玻璃的國家 <br />\n劃破世界貫耳的悲鳴<br />\n織出星塵變幻<br />\n<br />\n禁絕了悲憤  禁絕了抗爭<br />\n犯錯只因呼吸 寧願玉碎<br />\n當飛灰勝於浮塵<br />\n紅蓮未決我命運<br />\n多得你 再怕 手也未震"},{"pid":"9345980b6efd24e6805353f57df3e5afe41af8a5","tid":2356173,"uid":156861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb6bb24423f16752d700e61fda5f8b855e6ebf4","tid":2356173,"uid":64477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:31:51.000Z","msg":"支持狗巴"},{"pid":"7f9d47102e2b89b0a71d3c122c12c2c7486d07bf","tid":2356173,"uid":94021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661250d2d0c0dd99b9ac67c1563e85eb5e417eb0","tid":2356173,"uid":66909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06