/>\n扭曲世態 說穿已變 發現號擱淺<br />\n號角聲響起 <span class=\"red\">走失跟遠去</span> 迷霧伸出手挽救<br />\n<br />\n殘喘在世 屈膝呑聲 也未復舊時<br />\n從何時夢裡 輾轉反側 兩眼現淚印<br />\n行快數十年 盛世不要悼念<br />\n就算悲傷失意無力亦敢向前<br />\n<br />\n黑影滿地偏佈 被噤聲 繼續有我<br />\n炎夏再續嚴寒 絕處花也綻放 不會慌<br />\n<br />\n美夢裏驚詫 惡夢裏掙扎<br />\n結局也許比今天都更差<br />\n命裡偷生 苟且得今晨 他朝安然過吧<br />\n<br />\n濫捕再拘禁 噩耗試當真<br />\n直至呼吸消失 頑強面對<br />\n光閃過心底留痕 留存後世你重任<br />\n偏要逆風而行 再怕輸都要跟<br />\n蒼天也終答允 破我軀殼上惡咒<br />\n<br />\n多得你 始終未放手"},{"pid":"76a68563a38c0df270a7cd7cfb76002a52897e37","tid":2356173,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T17:52:19.000Z","msg":"最尾怪怪地 有機會再改<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a068b19db8fb2b605c55cdf481a9d3680f0674f4","tid":2356173,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T18:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eaaf0dc6a655391415ee7939f47dcbe2b1eb24b","tid":2356173,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52672c7e792dd03698c61bb0464d978a92f1a65","tid":2356173,"uid":385775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"43f4fe01be0e714f4c6450a6e5a4613bedbc998f","tid":2356173,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b52672c7e792dd03698c61bb0464d978a92f1a65","tid":2356173,"uid":385775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:36:44.000Z","msg":"原來你都改過 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b0ad831b75837e963db249102229c2cfb3f01a","tid":2356173,"uid":385775,"like":